summary: ...JERRY PASSING JUST EAST OF BARBUDA THIS EVENING... ...TROPICAL STORM WARNINGS REMAIN IN EFFECT FOR PORTIONS OF THE NORTHERN LEEWARD ISLANDS... As of 8:00 PM AST Thu Oct 09 the center of Jerry was located near 17.5, -61.1 with movement WNW at 18 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
